{"word":"G3888 - παραμυθέομαι - paramythéomai - par-am-oo-theh'-om-ahee - Comfort","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παραμυθέομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">paramythéomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-am-oo-theh'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Comfort</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஆறுதல் சொல், தேற்று"},{"paragraph":"to speak to one, to address one, to calm and to console"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and the middle of a derivative of <a href=\"#/G3454 - μῦθος - mŷthos - moo'-thos/3454\">G3454</a>; to <i>relate near</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>encourage</i>, <i>console:</i> - comfort.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3888/3888\">G3888</a>, <a href=\"#/G3889/3889\">G3889</a>, <a href=\"#/G3890/3890\">G3890</a>"}]}